subSubSection.paragraph:
Phaenochilus
metasternalis

Miyatake, 1970: 334; 
Pang and Mao 1979
: 78; 
Cao 1992
: 152; 
Ren et al. 2009
: 138.

Male genitalia: penis slender and long, outer arm of penis capsule slightly longer than inner arm, apex of penis with a small protuberances and membranous appendage inside (Fig. 3
e-f
). Tegmen stout, penis guide knife-like in ventral view (Fig. 3h). Parameres as long as penis guide with dense short setae at inner sides and apices with patches of short setae visible in lateral view (Fig. 3g).

